<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>

  <%- include('partial/head', { title: 'CAP 2032 — Une thèse en trois temps'}) %>

  <style>
    :root {
      --noir: #0d0d0d;
      --blanc: #f5f2eb;
      --ocre: #b5822a;
      --ocre-clair: #d4a85a;
      --gris: #6b6459;
      --gris-clair: #c8c0b0;
      --rouge: #8b2020;
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      background: var(--noir);
      color: var(--blanc);
      font-family: 'Source Serif 4', Georgia, serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* GRAIN OVERLAY */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 999;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
      padding: 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--ocre), transparent);
    }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 2rem 4rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.2);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(13,13,13,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--ocre);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: var(--ocre-clair);
    }

    /* HERO CONTENT */
    .hero-content {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 4rem 4rem 4rem 4rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: var(--ocre);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.2s;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.4s;
    }

    .hero-title em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--ocre-clair);
    }

    .hero-title .line-indent {
      padding-left: 6rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.6s;
    }

    .hero-subtitle strong {
      color: var(--blanc);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      align-items: center;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 0.8s;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--ocre);
      color: var(--noir);
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 400;
      transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--ocre-clair);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gris);
      padding-bottom: 2px;
      transition: color 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      color: var(--blanc);
      border-color: var(--blanc);
    }


    /* HERO FOOTER */
    .hero-footer {
      padding: 2rem 4rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      opacity: 0;
      animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease forwards 1s;
    }

    .hero-date {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--gris);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .scroll-hint {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--gris);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .scroll-line {
      width: 40px;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--gris);
      animation: scrollPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes scrollPulse {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.3; width: 40px; }
      50% { opacity: 1; width: 60px; }
    }

    /* URGENCE BAND */
    .urgence-band {
      background: var(--rouge);
      padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .urgence-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .urgence-ticker {
      display: flex;
      gap: 3rem;
      animation: ticker 30s linear infinite;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .urgence-ticker span {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
    }

    .urgence-ticker .sep {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    }

    @keyframes ticker {
      0% { transform: translateX(0); }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* INTRO SECTION */
    .intro {
      padding: 8rem 4rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
      gap: 6rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .intro-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.65rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: var(--ocre);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding-top: 0.5rem;
      position: sticky;
      top: 4rem;
    }

    .intro-text p {
      font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.8vw, 1.3rem);
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
    }

    .intro-text p strong {
      color: var(--blanc);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .intro-text p em {
      color: var(--ocre-clair);
      font-style: italic;
    }

    .intro-pullquote {
      border-left: 3px solid var(--ocre);
      padding: 1.5rem 0 1.5rem 2rem;
      margin: 2.5rem 0;
    }

    .intro-pullquote p {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.5rem) !important;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--blanc) !important;
      line-height: 1.5 !important;
    }

    /* TROIS PILIERS */
    .piliers {
      padding: 6rem 4rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.15);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.15);
    }

    .piliers-header {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto 5rem;
    }

    .piliers-eyebrow {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      color: var(--ocre);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .piliers-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.15;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .piliers-grid {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 0;
    }

    .pilier-card {
      padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.15);
      position: relative;
      transition: background 0.4s;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: block;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .pilier-card:last-child {
      border-right: none;
    }

    .pilier-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--ocre);
      transform: scaleX(0);
      transform-origin: left;
      transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }

    .pilier-card:hover {
      background: rgba(181,130,42,0.04);
    }

    .pilier-card:hover::before {
      transform: scaleX(1);
    }

    .pilier-num {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: rgba(181,130,42,0.2);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .pilier-tag {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--ocre);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .pilier-name {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .pilier-desc {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .pilier-themes {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .pilier-theme {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.3);
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .pilier-arrow {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2.5rem;
      right: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: var(--ocre);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateX(-8px);
      transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    .pilier-card:hover .pilier-arrow {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateX(0);
    }

    /* CHIFFRES CLÉS */
    .chiffres {
      padding: 7rem 4rem;
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .chiffres-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .chiffre-item {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.3);
      padding-top: 2rem;
    }

    .chiffre-num {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--ocre-clair);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .chiffre-label {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
    }

    /* Piliers secondaires*/

    .piliers-secondaires {
  padding: 6rem 4rem;
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

    /* DÉMARCHE */
    .demarche {
      padding: 7rem 4rem;
      background: rgba(181,130,42,0.04);
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.15);
    }

    .demarche-inner {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 8rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .demarche-text h2 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .demarche-text p {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .demarche-text p strong { color: var(--blanc); }

    .demarche-aside {
      border-left: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.3);
      padding-left: 3rem;
    }

    .demarche-aside-label {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em;
      color: var(--ocre);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      display: block;
    }

    .demarche-list {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .demarche-list li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--gris-clair);
      padding: 0.8rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .demarche-list li::before {
      content: '→';
      color: var(--ocre);
      flex-shrink: 0;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      margin-top: 0.1rem;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
      padding: 4rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.2);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .footer-logo {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--ocre);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .footer-credit {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--gris);
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .footer-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .footer-links a {
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: 0.6rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gris);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--ocre-clair); }

    /* ANIMATIONS */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(32px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }

    .reveal.visible {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero-content { padding: 3rem 2rem; }
      .hero-number { display: none; }
      .hero-footer { padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
      .urgence-band { padding: 1rem 2rem; }
      .intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 4rem 2rem; gap: 2rem; }
      .intro-label { position: static; }
      .piliers { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
      .piliers-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .pilier-card { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.15); }
      .chiffres { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
      .chiffres-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 2rem; }
      .demarche { padding: 4rem 2rem; }
      .demarche-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
      .demarche-aside { border-left: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,0.3); padding-left: 0; padding-top: 2rem; }
      footer { flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; text-align: center; padding: 3rem 2rem; }
    }

    /* ========================= */
/* PARCOURS UTILISATEUR */
/* ========================= */

.parcours {
  padding: 6rem 4rem;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(181,130,42,.15);
}

.parcours-steps {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 2rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

.step span {
  font-size: 2rem;
  color: var(--ocre);
}

/* ========================= */
/* PROGRESSION */
/* ========================= */

.progress-bar {
  height: 4px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
}

.progress-bar div {
  height: 100%;
  background: var(--ocre);
}

a:not(.btn-primary):not(.btn-secondary) {
  color: var(--ocre-clair);
}

a:not(.btn-primary):not(.btn-secondary):hover {
  color: var(--blanc);
}

.constat-inner {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
}

.constat-list {
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  font-size: 1.25rem;
}


  </style>

</head>
<body class="page-index">

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav>
    <span class="nav-logo">CAP 2032</span>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#parcours">Parcours en trois étapes</a></li>
      <li><a href="#piliers">Les trois angles</a></li>
      <li><a href="#demarche">La démarche</a></li>
      <li><a href="/ressources">Ressources</a></li>
      <li><a href="/notes">Notes stratégiques</a></li>
      <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">



    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Archéologie · Philosophie · Application contemporaine</p>

      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Gouverner dans un monde<br>
        <em>devenu systémique</em> ?
      </h1>

      <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Nos sociétés disposent de davantage d’informations, d’expertises et d’outils que jamais.<br>
          Pourtant, l’action publique paraît fragmentée, instable, souvent impuissante.<br><br>
          Ce travail propose une hypothèse simple : <strong>la crise n’est pas morale. Elle est structurelle.</strong><br>
          Et elle peut être pensée autrement.

      </p>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#piliers" class="btn-primary">Explorer la thèse</a>
        <a href="#demarche" class="btn-secondary">Comprendre la démarche</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-footer">
      <span class="hero-date">Christophe Louverture — 2025</span>
      <span class="scroll-hint">
        <span class="scroll-line"></span>
        Défiler
      </span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="constat">
    <div class="constat-inner">
      <p class="piliers-eyebrow">Constat</p>
      <ul class="constat-list">
        <li>Dette publique française : environ 3 200 milliards d’euros</li>
        <li>Désindustrialisation continue depuis les années 1980</li>
        <li>Fragmentation institutionnelle croissante</li>
        <li>Baisse durable de la confiance dans les institutions</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Parcours utilisateur-->

  <section class="parcours" id="parcours">
  <div class="parcours-inner">

    <p class="piliers-eyebrow">Par où commencer</p>

    <h2 class="parcours-title">Un parcours en trois étapes</h2>

    <div class="parcours-steps">

      <div class="step">
        <span>1</span>
        <h3>Comprendre</h3>
        <p>Explorer les fondements avec les piliers I et II.</p>
        <a href="/pilier1">Commencer →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <span>2</span>
        <h3>Structurer</h3>
        <p>Découvrir les 15 piliers du système.</p>
        <a href="#piliers-secondaires">Voir les piliers →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <span>3</span>
        <h3>Agir</h3>
        <p>Passer à l’action avec les prototypes.</p>
        <a href="/pilier3">Voir les prototypes →</a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>


  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section class="intro">
    <div class="intro-label">Pourquoi ce travail</div>
    <div class="intro-text">
      <p>Il y a un paradoxe au cœur de notre époque. <strong>Jamais nous n'avons eu autant de données, d'expertises, d'outils d'analyse.</strong> Et jamais l'action publique n'a semblé aussi hésitante, aussi fragmentée, aussi incapable de tenir une trajectoire.</p>

      <p>Les diagnostics s'accumulent. Les réformes s'annulent. Les alternances ne changent rien à la structure. Et pendant ce temps, <em>les problèmes, eux, deviennent systémiques</em> — énergétiques, agricoles, sociaux, institutionnels — et refusent d'être traités en silos.</p>

      <div class="intro-pullquote">
        <p>Ce qui manque n’est peut-être pas une réforme de plus, mais un cadre permettant de penser les interactions avant d’agir.</p>
      </div>

      <p>Ce travail ne prétend pas apporter des réponses définitives. Il propose un cadre : trois angles d'entrée dans une même question — <strong>comment les sociétés humaines ont-elles réussi à coopérer à grande échelle, et que faudrait-il pour que nous y parvenions à nouveau ?</strong></p>

      <p>C'est un travail né d'un parcours atypique — terrain, technique, humanitaire, agriculture — et d'une conviction : <strong>que le recul n'est pas une faiblesse. C'est une condition de la vision.</strong></p>
    </div>
  </section>

